Body:
Description: Hi Support, 

This is regarding an issue that occurred on customer's side. 
The status on the DC--> Computers list is reflected as "Licensed" and offline. But when we check the license list, we can see that there is not license occupied by that computer. 

My insights on this: PC which are not occupying license but marked as licensed in "Computers" list (DC), are mostly "Offline" for long time.

Total licensed computers are more in count than number if license occupied. 
Please assist on this. 

Thanks, 
Milan Singh

What We've Learned Updated: The status on the DC--> Computers list is reflected as "Licensed" and offline. But when we check the license list, we can see that there is not license occupied by that computer.
Computers which are not occupying license but are marked as licensed in "Computers" list (DC), are mostly "Offline" for long time.

Total licensed computers are more in count than number if license occupied.
Next Steps Updated: Releasing all computer licenses resolved the issue. Case can be closed.
